ActCanada Pension Plan
SubjectRegulations Amending the Canada Pension Plan Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADA PENSION PLAN REGULATIONS in order to prescribe the form and manner in which an election (to stop contributing) or a revocation of a prior election (to restart contributions) must be made and to extend the time limit for payment of contributions resulting from an election made in relation to self-employed earnings.
